<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1042413" n="1"/> 
<opener>
  <lb/><dateline>Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> d. 13. <abbr>Febr.</abbr> <abbr>A.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> 1704.</dateline>
  <lb/>Salutem cum officiis.

    <lb/>Excellentissime et Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clarissime Domine Professor!</opener>

  <p><lb/>Mult<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m, Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clarissime Vir, me Tibi debere fateor, tum quod ante
    <lb/>biennium, et quod excurrit, <rs type="person">Filio</rs> meo in suo itinere haud exigua
    <lb/>et benevolenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> et Hospitalitatis exhibuisti beneficia, tum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#oacut">ó</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>d ex
    <lb/>eo tempore Tuo affectu ipsum ade<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> dignatus, ut amicissimas quando<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
    <lb/>ad eum dederis <rs type="letter">literas</rs>; Quibus omnibus nunc etiam novus iste Humanita<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> accessit cumulus, ut ipsi honorific<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> alicujus Stationis Spem facias,
    <lb/>Mathematicas literas (ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> natus esse videtur) docendi; qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, si<del><gap/></del>
    <lb/>obtingeret, non sol<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m ipsi, sed etiam mihi, (qui Divin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> voluntati, ipsum ad
    <lb/>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c studia docenda vocanti minim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> repugnare volo, nam concionibus habendis
    <lb/>eum min<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>s aptum video), gratissima esset res; Quare hoc nomine Te <abbr>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>clariss.</abbr> <abbr><choice><orig>DNE</orig><reg>Dne</reg></choice></abbr>, vehementer rogo, ut in coepto opere pergere, meum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <rs type="person">filium</rs>
    <lb/>quum optim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> Tibi commendatum porr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> esse velis, cert<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>s ipsum sedul<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> da<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>turum operam, ut Spartam, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>m pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>vi<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> legitim<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vocatione accipiet,
    <lb/>per <choice><orig>DEI</orig><reg>Dei</reg></choice> gratiam ita sit exornaturus, ut Vir <abbr>Claris.</abbr> su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> istius commen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dationis non poeniteat, me<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> <rs type="person">filium</rs> (ali<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>s jam Ipsi obligatissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mos) arctius sibi devinciat. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum ut Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> surgenti in <rs type="place">patri<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></rs> digni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tati l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus applaudo; Sic et felicissim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <add>suo tempore</add> Te administrari, et ut amplior
    <lb/>et magnis Tuis meritis dignior brevi succedat, toto pectore opto;
    <lb/>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea Ornatissimam <rs type="person">thori Sociam</rs> cum dulcissimis <rs type="person">Liberis</rs> pluri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>m<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m cum Viro Excellentissimo salvere et valere iubeo, qui sum <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> ero</p>
<closer>
  <lb/>Excellenti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>

    <salute><lb/>humillimus <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> studiosissimus
    <lb/>servus ac Cultor</salute>
    <lb/><signed>Germanus Hermannus</signed> G<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>mnasiarch<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>.</closer>
  <pb facs="1042414" n="2" type="empty"/>
</div>
